title: Google officially expands Pixel 6 and Pixel 6 Pro sales to Singapore
content:
Google’s Pixel 6 series has been somewhat of a hit since launch, despite the phones being sold in limited regions. After expanding in Europe earlier this month, Google is now opening up sales of the Pixel 6 and Pixel 6 Pro in Singapore.

more…

The post Google officially expands Pixel 6 and Pixel 6 Pro sales to Singapore appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: Google has officially launched the Pixel 6 and Pixel 6 Pro in Singapore, making the phones available for sale in 12 total countries.
